resources.string:
Elements in the Markup toolbar:<br>\t1. Go to the list of selected words;   
        	<br>\t2. Add/Remove the bookmark on the top line;
        	<br>\t3. View a list of bookmarks (to go to one of them);
        	<br>\t4. Clear marks, bookmarks, a List of words;
        	<br>\t5. It is the bookmark;
        	<br>\t6. It is the markred word.

Elements in the List Of Words toolbar:<br>\t1. Go to the Markup;   
        	<br>\t2. Clear marks, bookmarks, a List of words;
        	<br>\t3. Update translation (for example, after a change of dictionary);
        	<br>\t4. When you select a row in the list opens the full text dictionary translation.

Elements in the Dictionary toolbar:<br>\t1.  Go to the List Of Words;   
        	<br>\t2. Select external Dictionary;
        	<br>\t3. Select a built-in dictionary.
